<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/601712-why-do-the-villains-try-to-cause-a-tsunami">Why do the villains try to cause a tsunami wave? Is anyone arguing that climate change will cause more earthquakes, as Crichton implies, or is he just confused?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_601712'><a id="like_count_community_question_601712" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/601712?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F15860.State_of_Fear">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
