      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1749610-state-of-fear">Quotes from State of Fear</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Do you know what we call opinion in the absence of evidence? We call it prejudice.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
